Billion Dollar Secret



Company Summary
Inrad Optics Inc. develops, manufactures and markets products and services for use in photonics industry sectors. The Company's product areas include crystals and crystal components, custom optics, systems and instruments, and thin film services. The products produced by Inrad Optics, Inc. fall into two main categories: Optical Components and Laser System Devices and Instrumentation. The Optical Components segment is focused on custom optics manufacturing. The Laser System Devices and Instrumentation category includes the growth and fabrication of crystalline materials with electro-optic and non-linear optical properties for use in both standard and custom products. It serves the defense, aerospace, laser systems, process control and metrology sectors of the photonics industry, U.S. Government, National Laboratories and Universities worldwide. Inrad Optics Inc., formerly known as Photonic Products Group, Inc., is headquartered in Northvale, New Jersey.   

















 




















	Inrad Optics Inc. | Photonics Buyers' Guide







































